ey discovers that he can hear the voices of the killer’s previous victims. And they are dead set on making sure that what happened to them doesn’t happen to Finney.","genre_ids":[27,53],"popularity":10.3834,"vote_count":5674,"poster_path":"/p9ZUzCyy9wRTDuuQexkQ78R2BgF.jpg","release_date":"2022-06-16","vote_average":7.535,"backdrop_path":"/AfvIjhDu9p64jKcmohS4hsPG95Q.jpg","original_title":"The Black Phone","original_language":"en"},{"id":113523,"adult":false,"title":"Doomsday Machine","video":false,"overview":"Following the discovery of a doomsday machine capable of destroying Earth, the launch of a US space mission to Venus is taken over by the military.","genre_ids":[878],"popularity":0.4665,"vote_count":32,"poster_path":"/8K2Xho8yK3bFGTCuZcc5Qo420dp.jpg","release_date":"1972-01-01","vote_average":3.109,"backdrop_path":"/m3EKZKunYksXMNU11lxd8dYxcmy.jpg","original_title":"Doomsday Machine","original_language":"en"},{"id":367882,"adult":false,"title":"The Phone","video":false,"overview":"When his wife is murdered, Dong-ho loses the light in his life, breaks down and falls into depression. But he knows that as long as the killer is still around, he can not get out of his loss. Then, one day, he receives a call and can not believe who he is listening to.","genre_ids":[53,28,9648],"popularity":0.5265,"vote_count":51,"poster_path":"/rXslVikPfGoO0ip0Z32Ap23gxea.jpg","release_date":"2015-10-22","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/1T38HmiO1C2qQS6yrGPi8g8ygI5.jpg","original_title":"더 폰","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1362374,"adult":false,"title":"Purgatory Station","video":false,"overview":"When a crooked lawyer wakes up in a large, pitch-dark container, he learns he has eight hours to scuttle a corporate land grab or see everyone he loves die horribly.","genre_ids":[53,18],"popularity":1.1188,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/xf9qrzAe5DgM0z6DBDLJ8aoP7im.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-29","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/ziyUBUwrN8nunKTd8LEvwyMM9UV.jpg","original_title":"Purgatory Station","original_language":"en"},{"id":114174,"adult":false,"title":"Scalps","video":false,"overview":"The commander of a Texan fort in the Civil War refuses to surrender to the Northerners, and tries to buy the local Indian tribe chief's daughter. The sage man refuses, and the Southerners massacre the tribe and abduct the young squaw anyway. The noble squaw manages to escape, and hides out with a rough rancher, who dislikes Indians, but hates the Southerners more. The odd couple joins forces, and tactics, to exert ultimate vengeance on the men at the fort.","genre_ids":[37,28,18],"popularity":0.3265,"vote_count":23,"poster_path":"/4IrBuNkb5exTxypzDkeYJ91j80u.jpg","release_date":"1987-10-14","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/s37Wg0kGG4zJM0OpwotcsB8MTHG.jpg","original_title":"Scalps","original_language":"it"},{"id":114285,"adult":false,"title":"Everybody Has a Plan","video":false,"overview":"Pedro, a humble beekeeper who lives in the mysterious Argentinian region of the Delta del Tigre, travels to Buenos Aires to visit his twin brother Agustín, a successful but troubled pediatrician with marital issues, to give him bad news and ask him for a favor hard to fulfill, a unexpected arrival which will change Agustín's life forever.","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":0.329,"vote_count":34,"poster_path":"/ub01cFc8V7KdNpJiQOxaqpbu4kN.jpg","release_date":"2012-08-30","vote_average":4.6,"backdrop_path":"/ntGL1dRDgdtbwf4TiBLeIhlBibW.jpg","original_title":"Todos tenemos un plan","original_language":"es"},{"id":357940,"adult":false,"title":"Mr. Six","video":false,"overview":"Many years ago Mr. Six was a notorious gangster. That was back when there was still such a thing as honour among thieves, when criminals earned respect and maintained principles. These days Mr. Six is all but forgotten, a living relic residing in a narrow alley.  One day Six's son, Xiaobo, is abducted by some spoiled punks after he scratches their precious Ferrari. Mr. Six realizes that he must do whatever it takes to get his son back — even if that means returning to the life he thought he had left behind.","genre_ids":[80,28,18],"popularity":1.1638,"vote_count":168,"poster_path":"/hVttIfMDjQwHdVpUYhxdBamkl02.jpg","release_date":"2015-12-18","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/dWE2Ja6FSMIBZgiBXGv30RCo1hh.jpg","original_title":"老炮儿","original_language":"zh"},{"id":357705,"adult":false,"title":"Phoenix Point","video":false,"overview":"When the apocalypse arrives, it takes the form of a biochemical virus. All social structures break down and a new world order emerges from the heart of the desert. As chaos sets in, we follow the adventures of some unlikely survivors, all searching for the elusive cure at Phoenix Point.","genre_ids":[878],"popularity":0.2101,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/ngPykHAmDdsiOxdNE20YXZukQk4.jpg","release_date":"2005-01-20","vote_average":2.2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Phoenix Point","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt7737786","twitter_id":"GreenlandMovie","facebook_id":"GreenlandMovie","wikidata_id":"Q73897733","instagram_id":"greenlandmovie","metacritic_id":"movie/greenland","mydramalist_id":"342666","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/greenland"},"social_ids":{"twitter":"GreenlandMovie","facebook":"GreenlandMovie","instagram":"greenlandmovie"},"gdvg_id":100067,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AU","release_dates":[{"note":"Amazon Prime Video","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2021-04-02T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"M"},{"note":"","type":5,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2021-05-31T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"M"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"BE","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2020-07-29T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"